    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for any buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine and no imperfections, scratches, or dings. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that looks and feels like new and all electronic components functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no issues to report. This is a collector-grade vehicle that offers a like-new driving experience.",
