      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a gem. This beauty has been my reliable companion for weekend cruises and grocery runs alike. She\u2019s got that classic soul and drives like a dream\u2014smooth, responsive, and always ready for the next adventure. I\u2019ve kept her well-fed with top-shelf oil and plenty of TLC. Now, she\u2019s got a couple of tiny 'character marks' from her travels, but honestly, they just show she\u2019s been loved. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, honest ride that\u2019ll put a smile on your face every time you turn the key, you\u2019ve found it. Come say hi and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted performance machine that bridges the gap between raw power and mechanical refinement. The high-revving powerplant exhibits exceptional thermal management and linear power delivery, with no evidence of oil aeration or timing variance. I've personally overseen the preventative maintenance schedule, ensuring the cooling system's pressure remains nominal and the drivetrain's torsional rigidity is preserved. The suspension geometry is tight, featuring refreshed bushings that eliminate deflection under heavy cornering loads. Gear engagement is crisp across the gates with zero synchro drag, reflecting a gearbox that has been treated with respect. This vehicle is mechanically dialed-in and ready for the most demanding technical roads.",
      "price": 38900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    }
